Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:36.03,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\blur4\fad(600,0)\3c&H000000&\pos(780,570)}Friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean to say that only rookies\Nwent after Sasuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It really couldn't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.77,0:01:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the situation in\Nthe Village being how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've taken the minimally\Nrequired measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mission has already\Nbeen assigned!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'm gonna go do an errand\Nand will be back shortly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already been two days\Nsince Sasuke left the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And Naruto and the others who went in\Npursuit haven't come back either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And neither has Lee...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I've more or less\Nheard the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.79,0:02:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I... believe in Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe him, but if something were\Nto happen to Naruto and Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.01,0:02:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura, you don't need to\Nworry about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Summoning Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I want you guys to\Nfan out in all directions
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in pursuit of Naruto\Nand Sasuke's scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto and Sasuke you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen\Nto the two of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain later...\NRight now, time is of essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as you confirm that\Nyou've detected the scent,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,call me and I'll be there immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess since she saw them\Nfight before her very eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,it's useless to tell her\Nnot to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke... Stop with revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you were successful\Nin carrying out your revenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,all that will come out of it\Nis a sense of emptiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:04:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that so knowingly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither you nor I could\Ncall ourselves lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Of that much I'm certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But it could be worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Both you and I have found\Nprecious comrades, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We understand that all the more\Nbecause we've lost them once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I taught you Chidori
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,because you now have\Nprecious people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That power isn't something to be used\Nagainst your comrades or for revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what that power\Nshould be used for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna win no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too naive...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Watching them, they might actually\Nbe intent on killing each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me get there in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I already said this earlier but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In truth, you were waiting\Nfor this too, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither Kakashi nor Sakura\Nare present right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's nobody here to stop us\Nlike that time before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This time around we're gonna\Nsettle this for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Chidori!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here!\NI'm gonna clobber you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and take you back home even\Nif I have to drag you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Rasengan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't meaningless...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, you became\Nmy closest friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke actually came out\Nand said that... to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's exactly the reason why\NI wanted to verify it using this Rasengan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.84,0:09:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He was able to counter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,my full power of Chidori\Nto that extent...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto, to what extent...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That loser...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, your limit is two blows...\Nthat's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I try to use more than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,what will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The third blow won't initiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you try to initiate\Nthe Jutsu forcibly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,not only will the Art not\Ninitiate properly,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but your Chakra will become zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.22,0:10:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In the worst case scenario\Nit will cost you your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... I can't waste a blow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't serve any purpose\Nif we cancel each other like earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's... no longer\Nany mistake about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.34,0:11:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You... really intended...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You really intended to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I will use numerous speedy techniques\Nand Jutsu to create an opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And then... I will make\Na hit with Chidori.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know, Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Top-class Ninja should be\Nable to read each other's hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,simply by an exchange of fists.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without saying anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're naive, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you really able\Nto read inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,this heart of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Style:\NPhoenix Flower Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke... I knew that you\Nwere always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I was relieved\Nwhen I found out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that there was\Na guy similar to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And it also made me happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, I really wanted\Nto approach you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I wasn't able to approach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- Awesome...\N- You're incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You were always able\Nto do everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And moreover, you were always\Nbeing praised by everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you and I\Nwere so different...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I didn't want to admit it,\NI decided to call you my rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to lose to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and I felt that even more strongly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,because I was called a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when we were\Nin the Squad Seven,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I continued to feel\Nthe same way the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And wasn't able to express\Nwhat I really felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What I really wanted was\Nto become like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You were what I aspired to... so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You are one of the ones\NI want to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really happy when\Nyou said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were your first words...\Nacknowledging me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I both knew,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,without us even having to\Nhave an exchange of fists!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,From that time on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without saying anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,we are friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not without meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To me you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,my closest friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,However... you're trying to\Ntake me down for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I don't really know
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:16:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,whether you really meant\Nwhat you said earlier or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking that we were friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That might have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That might have been just me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,really lame, aren't I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped, can it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,don't want you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you to be taken away\Nby someone like Orochimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You managed to divert it\Nwith your left hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to use\Nany hand sign
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,or that Jutsu earlier anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that red Chakra...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does he get that\Nkind of power from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the heck... is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,His shoulder injury is healing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke! I'm not gonna let\NOrochimaru take you away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I will stop you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:21:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,even if I have to break every bone\Nin your arms and legs!
Comment: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:07.78,ED9,,0,0,0,,ED Start
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.24,0:21:18.07,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}When I recalled the parts one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:24.44,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}I felt as though I had understood everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:35.01,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Faded words which I kept so close to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:44.79,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Speechless nights, a hint of warmth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:51.53,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}and this distant yearning for you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:22:00.84,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}I live, simply repeating this cycle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.02,0:22:12.55,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Held in my two hands is a droplet of time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:23.00,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Softly clutching forgotten memories, lost words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:36.80,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}{\fad(0,2500)}I'll keep these thoughts...
Comment: 0,0:22:37.74,0:22:37.80,ED9,,0,0,0,,ED End
